            <description><![CDATA[<h2>Tempora 0.2.2</h2>
<ul>
    <li><b>Fixed</b> — Calendar integration now shows your calendars and the timeline calendar lane again. When calendar access hadn't been granted yet, an already-enabled integration would silently show no calendars and no lane; Tempora now prompts for access on the Calendar settings tab and refreshes as soon as access is granted.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
